# Table Component Patterns

> TDS 테이블 상세 Props: `04-tds-detail-catalog.mdc` 참조, 금지 패턴 요약: `03-tds-essentials.mdc` 참조

## 테이블 종류 선택 기준

| 컴포넌트 | 사용 조건 |
|----------|-----------|
| `Table` | 단순 목록, 선택 불필요 |
| `SelectableTable` | 체크박스 벌크 선택 필요 |

## Column 정의 패턴

### COLUMN_KEYS 상수

```typescript
const COLUMN_KEYS = {
  STATUS: 'status',
  NAME: 'name',
  TYPE: 'type',
  ACTIONS: 'actions',
} as const;
```

### columns + columnMap

```tsx
const columns: TableColumn[] = useMemo(
  () => [
    { key: COLUMN_KEYS.STATUS, header: t('table.status'), width: 70, align: 'center', sortable: false },
    { key: COLUMN_KEYS.NAME, header: t('table.name'), sortable: true },
    { key: COLUMN_KEYS.ACTIONS, header: t('table.action'), width: 72, align: 'center', sortable: false },
  ],
  [t],
);

const columnMap = useMemo(
  () => Object.fromEntries(columns.map((c) => [c.key, c])) as Record<string, TableColumn>,
  [columns],
);
```

## Status 매핑

도메인 Status → TDS `StatusIndicator` variant 매핑 상수:

```typescript
import { StatusIndicator } from '@thakicloud/shared';

const STATUS_TO_VARIANT: Record<DomainStatus, string> = {
  Running: 'active',
  Pending: 'pending',
  Failed: 'error',
  Stopped: 'suspended',
};
```

## Row 렌더링

### Table.Tr + Table.Td

```tsx
<Table.Tr key={entity.id} rowData={rowData}>
  <Table.Td column={columnMap[COLUMN_KEYS.STATUS]} rowData={rowData}>
    <Tooltip content={entity.status} direction="top">
      <StatusIndicator variant={STATUS_TO_VARIANT[entity.status]} />
    </Tooltip>
  </Table.Td>

  <Table.Td column={columnMap[COLUMN_KEYS.NAME]} rowData={rowData}>
    <span className="text-12 font-medium text-text truncate">{entity.name}</span>
  </Table.Td>

  {/* 액션 셀: preventClickPropagation 필수 */}
  <Table.Td column={columnMap[COLUMN_KEYS.ACTIONS]} rowData={rowData} preventClickPropagation>
    <Button variant="error" appearance="outline" size="xs" onClick={() => onDelete(entity)}>
      {t('actions.delete')}
    </Button>
  </Table.Td>
</Table.Tr>
```

### rowData 캐스팅

Table 컴포넌트가 `Record<string, unknown>` 요구:

```tsx
const rowData = entity as unknown as Record<string, unknown>;
```

## SelectableTable Props

```tsx
<SelectableTable
  rows={entities as unknown as Record<string, unknown>[]}
  columns={columns}
  selectionType="checkbox"
  selectedRows={selectedIds ?? []}
  onRowSelectionChange={onSelectionChange}
  getRowId={(row) => (row as unknown as DomainEntity).id}
  isLoading={loading}
  stickyLastColumn
  selectOnRowClick={false}
  emptyUI={emptyUI}
>
  {entities.map((entity) => (
    <Table.Tr key={entity.id} rowData={...}>...</Table.Tr>
  ))}
</SelectableTable>
```

## Empty State (테이블)

테이블 빈 상태는 `EmptyUI` 직접 사용 (테이블이 컨테이너 제공):

```tsx
const emptyUI = useMemo(
  () => (
    <EmptyUI
      content={{
        title: t('section.list.empty'),
        description: t('section.list.emptyDescription'),
      }}
    />
  ),
  [t],
);

<Table emptyUI={emptyUI}>...</Table>
```

## 금지

| 금지 패턴 | 올바른 패턴 |
|-----------|------------|
| column key 문자열 하드코딩 | `COLUMN_KEYS` 상수 사용 |
| `columns` 없이 `columnMap`만 사용 | `columns` → `columnMap` 파생 |
| 액션 셀에 `preventClickPropagation` 누락 | 반드시 추가 |
| `selectOnRowClick={true}` + `Table.Tr onClick` 동시 | `selectOnRowClick={false}` 후 onClick |
| `EmptyStatePanel` (테이블 내부) | `EmptyUI` (border 없는 버전) |

